{"id":"the-runaway-kite","slug":"the-runaway-kite","title":"The Runaway Kite","title_ko":"도망간 연","level":"A2","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/cover.webp","summary_ko":"줄이 끊어져 날아간 연을 쫓아 마을 곳곳을 누비며 친절한 이웃을 만나는 하루.","wordCount":190,"pages":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Mina had a red kite with a long tail.","translation_ko":"미나에게는 꼬리가 긴 빨간 연이 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mina","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"had","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":460,"endMs":760},{"word":"a","charStart":9,"charEnd":10,"startMs":760,"endMs":1020},{"word":"red","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1200},{"word":"kite","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1500},{"word":"with","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1760},{"word":"a","charStart":25,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2120},{"word":"long","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2240},{"word":"tail","charStart":32,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2240,"endMs":2580}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"She flew it in the park on a windy day.","translation_ko":"바람 부는 날, 미나는 공원에서 그 연을 날렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"flew","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":240,"endMs":480},{"word":"it","charStart":9,"charEnd":11,"startMs":480,"endMs":720},{"word":"in","charStart":12,"charEnd":14,"startMs":720,"endMs":800},{"word":"the","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":800,"endMs":920},{"word":"park","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":920,"endMs":1220},{"word":"on","charStart":24,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1380},{"word":"a","charStart":27,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1540},{"word":"windy","charStart":29,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1740},{"word":"day","charStart":35,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2060}]}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"The wind grew strong, and the string pulled hard.","translation_ko":"바람이 거세지자 줄이 팽팽하게 당겨졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":200},{"word":"wind","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":200,"endMs":420},{"word":"grew","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":420,"endMs":720},{"word":"strong","charStart":14,"charEnd":20,"startMs":720,"endMs":1160},{"word":"and","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1680},{"word":"the","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1680,"endMs":1920},{"word":"string","charStart":30,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2120},{"word":"pulled","charStart":37,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2420},{"word":"hard","charStart":44,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2740}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"Then the string snapped, and the kite flew away.","translation_ko":"그때 줄이 툭 끊어지더니 연이 날아가 버렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"the","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":420,"endMs":760},{"word":"string","charStart":9,"charEnd":15,"startMs":760,"endMs":1060},{"word":"snapped","charStart":16,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1480},{"word":"and","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1480,"endMs":2020},{"word":"the","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2300},{"word":"kite","charStart":33,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2340},{"word":"flew","charStart":38,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2340,"endMs":2620},{"word":"away","charStart":43,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2620,"endMs":2900}]}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"Wait, come back!\" Mina shouted.","translation_ko":"\"기다려, 돌아와!\" 미나가 소리쳤어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Wait","charStart":1,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":740},{"word":"come","charStart":7,"charEnd":11,"startMs":840,"endMs":1300},{"word":"back","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1620},{"word":"Mina","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":2160,"endMs":2220},{"word":"shouted","charStart":24,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2580}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"She ran after it because she did not want to lose it.","translation_ko":"연을 잃고 싶지 않아서 미나는 그것을 뒤쫓아 달렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"ran","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":360,"endMs":640},{"word":"after","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":640,"endMs":1020},{"word":"it","charStart":14,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1260},{"word":"because","charStart":17,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1740},{"word":"she","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1740,"endMs":1980},{"word":"did","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2120},{"word":"not","charStart":33,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2400},{"word":"want","charStart":37,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2400,"endMs":2640},{"word":"to","charStart":42,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2640,"endMs":2840},{"word":"lose","charStart":45,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2840,"endMs":2960},{"word":"it","charStart":50,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2960,"endMs":3160}]}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"The kite landed on a wooden fence near a garden.","translation_ko":"연은 정원 옆 나무 울타리에 내려앉았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"kite","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":240,"endMs":580},{"word":"landed","charStart":9,"charEnd":15,"startMs":580,"endMs":1160},{"word":"on","charStart":16,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1440},{"word":"a","charStart":19,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1700},{"word":"wooden","charStart":21,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1700,"endMs":1800},{"word":"fence","charStart":28,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2220},{"word":"near","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2620},{"word":"a","charStart":39,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2620,"endMs":3040},{"word":"garden","charStart":41,"charEnd":47,"startMs":3040,"endMs":3040}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"When Mina reached for it, the wind lifted it.","translation_ko":"미나가 손을 뻗자 바람이 연을 들어 올렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"When","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"Mina","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":280,"endMs":540},{"word":"reached","charStart":10,"charEnd":17,"startMs":540,"endMs":900},{"word":"for","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":900,"endMs":1180},{"word":"it","charStart":22,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1320},{"word":"the","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1620},{"word":"wind","charStart":30,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1880},{"word":"lifted","charStart":35,"charEnd":41,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2220},{"word":"it","charStart":42,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2400}]}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"The kite floated up to a low rooftop.","translation_ko":"연은 낮은 지붕 위로 두둥실 떠올랐어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"kite","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":380,"endMs":520},{"word":"floated","charStart":9,"charEnd":16,"startMs":520,"endMs":920},{"word":"up","charStart":17,"charEnd":19,"startMs":920,"endMs":1180},{"word":"to","charStart":20,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1360},{"word":"a","charStart":23,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1560},{"word":"low","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1760},{"word":"rooftop","charStart":29,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2040}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"An old man saw it and waved.","translation_ko":"한 할아버지가 그것을 보고 손을 흔들었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"An","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":200},{"word":"old","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":200,"endMs":580},{"word":"man","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":580,"endMs":900},{"word":"saw","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":900,"endMs":1160},{"word":"it","charStart":15,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1340},{"word":"and","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1920},{"word":"waved","charStart":22,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1920,"endMs":1940}]}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"I will help you,\" he said with a kind smile.","translation_ko":"\"내가 도와줄게.\" 할아버지가 다정하게 웃으며 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"I","charStart":1,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"will","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":220,"endMs":520},{"word":"help","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":520,"endMs":800},{"word":"you","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":800,"endMs":1440},{"word":"he","charStart":19,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1640},{"word":"said","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1840},{"word":"with","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1840,"endMs":1980},{"word":"a","charStart":32,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2140},{"word":"kind","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2140,"endMs":2440},{"word":"smile","charStart":39,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2880}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"He used a long broom to push it down.","translation_ko":"할아버지는 긴 빗자루로 연을 아래로 밀어 주었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"used","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":220,"endMs":500},{"word":"a","charStart":8,"charEnd":9,"startMs":500,"endMs":740},{"word":"long","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":740,"endMs":1020},{"word":"broom","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1260},{"word":"to","charStart":21,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1540},{"word":"push","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1700},{"word":"it","charStart":29,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1700,"endMs":1880},{"word":"down","charStart":32,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2140}]}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"The kite slipped away and got caught in a tall tree.","translation_ko":"연은 다시 미끄러져 키 큰 나무에 걸렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"kite","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":260,"endMs":500},{"word":"slipped","charStart":9,"charEnd":16,"startMs":500,"endMs":1020},{"word":"away","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1400},{"word":"and","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1940},{"word":"got","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2140},{"word":"caught","charStart":30,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2140,"endMs":2440},{"word":"in","charStart":37,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2780},{"word":"a","charStart":40,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2780,"endMs":3000},{"word":"tall","charStart":42,"charEnd":46,"startMs":3000,"endMs":3160},{"word":"tree","charStart":47,"charEnd":51,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3380}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"Two children were playing there.","translation_ko":"그곳에서는 아이 둘이 놀고 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Two","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"children","charStart":4,"charEnd":12,"startMs":340,"endMs":920},{"word":"were","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":920,"endMs":1320},{"word":"playing","charStart":18,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1620},{"word":"there","charStart":26,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1900}]}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"A tall boy climbed up and shook the branch gently.","translation_ko":"키 큰 남자아이가 올라가 나뭇가지를 살살 흔들었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":0,"charEnd":1,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1600},{"word":"tall","charStart":2,"charEnd":6,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1880},{"word":"boy","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2140},{"word":"climbed","charStart":11,"charEnd":18,"startMs":2140,"endMs":2500},{"word":"up","charStart":19,"charEnd":21,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2780},{"word":"and","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":2780,"endMs":3060},{"word":"shook","charStart":26,"charEnd":31,"startMs":3060,"endMs":3220},{"word":"the","charStart":32,"charEnd":35,"startMs":3220,"endMs":3440},{"word":"branch","charStart":36,"charEnd":42,"startMs":3440,"endMs":3740},{"word":"gently","charStart":43,"charEnd":49,"startMs":3740,"endMs":4140}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"The kite fell, and his sister caught it.","translation_ko":"연이 떨어지자 그의 여동생이 받아 냈어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"kite","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":300,"endMs":480},{"word":"fell","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":480,"endMs":840},{"word":"and","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1300},{"word":"his","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1460},{"word":"sister","charStart":23,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1840},{"word":"caught","charStart":30,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2260},{"word":"it","charStart":37,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2480}]}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p9","pageNo":9,"spread":"p9","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p9.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p9-s1","ord":0,"text":"They passed the kite back to Mina.","translation_ko":"아이들은 연을 미나에게 다시 건네주었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p9-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":640},{"word":"passed","charStart":5,"charEnd":11,"startMs":640,"endMs":960},{"word":"the","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":960,"endMs":1400},{"word":"kite","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1460},{"word":"back","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1800},{"word":"to","charStart":26,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2060},{"word":"Mina","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2240}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p9-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Thank you so much!\" Mina said happily.","translation_ko":"\"정말 고마워!\" 미나가 환하게 웃으며 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p9-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Thank","charStart":1,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":480},{"word":"you","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":480,"endMs":720},{"word":"so","charStart":11,"charEnd":13,"startMs":720,"endMs":900},{"word":"much","charStart":14,"charEnd":18,"startMs":900,"endMs":1880},{"word":"Mina","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1880,"endMs":1920},{"word":"said","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2200},{"word":"happily","charStart":31,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2560}]}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p10","pageNo":10,"spread":"p10","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p10.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p10-s1","ord":0,"text":"They tied a new string to the kite.","translation_ko":"이웃들이 연에 새 줄을 묶어 주었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p10-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":680},{"word":"tied","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":680,"endMs":1040},{"word":"a","charStart":10,"charEnd":11,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1300},{"word":"new","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1580},{"word":"string","charStart":16,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1840},{"word":"to","charStart":23,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2080},{"word":"the","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2420},{"word":"kite","charStart":30,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2440}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p10-s2","ord":1,"text":"When the wind blew, the kite rose into the sky again.","translation_ko":"바람이 불자 연은 다시 하늘로 솟아올랐어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p10-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"When","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"the","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":220,"endMs":480},{"word":"wind","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":480,"endMs":740},{"word":"blew","charStart":14,"charEnd":18,"startMs":740,"endMs":1200},{"word":"the","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1980},{"word":"kite","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2080},{"word":"rose","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2540},{"word":"into","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2540,"endMs":2780},{"word":"the","charStart":39,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2780,"endMs":3100},{"word":"sky","charStart":43,"charEnd":46,"startMs":3100,"endMs":3320},{"word":"again","charStart":47,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3320,"endMs":3780}]}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p11","pageNo":11,"spread":"p11","imageUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/p11.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p11-s1","ord":0,"text":"Mina smiled because her neighbors had helped.","translation_ko":"이웃들이 도와주어서 미나는 흐뭇하게 웃었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p11-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mina","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"smiled","charStart":5,"charEnd":11,"startMs":400,"endMs":1100},{"word":"because","charStart":12,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1660},{"word":"her","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1660,"endMs":1920},{"word":"neighbors","charStart":24,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2200},{"word":"had","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2520},{"word":"helped","charStart":38,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2520,"endMs":2800}]},{"id":"the-runaway-kite-p11-s2","ord":1,"text":"Her kite was safe, and she had new friends.","translation_ko":"이제 연도 무사했고, 미나에게는 새 친구가 생겼어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-runaway-kite/audio/p11-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Her","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"kite","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":460,"endMs":780},{"word":"was","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":780,"endMs":1200},{"word":"safe","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1580},{"word":"and","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2280},{"word":"she","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2480},{"word":"had","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2480,"endMs":2640},{"word":"new","charStart":31,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2640,"endMs":2940},{"word":"friends","charStart":35,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2940,"endMs":3260}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"미나의 연은 어떤 모습이었나요?","type":"mc","options":["꼬리가 긴 빨간 연","작고 파란 연","별 모양 연","노란 풍선"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"미나에게는 꼬리가 긴 새빨간 연이 있었어요.","id":"the-runaway-kite-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"연이 날아간 까닭은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["미나가 일부러 놓아서","줄이 끊어져서","비가 와서","새가 물고 가서"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"바람이 거세져 줄이 툭 끊어지면서 연이 날아갔어요.","id":"the-runaway-kite-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"지붕 위의 연을 할아버지는 어떻게 내려 주었나요?","type":"mc","options":["사다리로 올라가서","긴 빗자루로 밀어서","돌을 던져서","물을 뿌려서"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"할아버지는 긴 빗자루로 연을 아래로 밀어 주었어요.","id":"the-runaway-kite-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"나무에 걸린 연을 누가 도와주었나요?","type":"mc","options":["미나의 엄마","공원 관리인","나무 아래에서 놀던 두 아이","지나가던 강아지"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"나무 아래에서 놀던 남자아이가 가지를 흔들고 여동생이 연을 받았어요.","id":"the-runaway-kite-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 전하려는 마음은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["혼자 하는 일이 가장 쉽다","이웃이 서로 도우면 어려운 일도 풀린다","연은 위험하니 날리면 안 된다","바람은 늘 무섭다"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"온 동네 이웃이 힘을 모아 도와준 덕분에 연을 되찾았어요.","id":"the-runaway-kite-q5","ord":4}]}